node.text: Day 14 of skiing with these esteemed gentlemen! Their shredding prowess is exponentially increasing.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Shay Butler ⛷ on January 26, 2021 tagging @colettekati, @daveramsey, and @aviacolette. May be an image of standing, food and car.

node.text: I bought my first car with cash when I was 16. I saved for a year and washed dishes 5 nights a week, most nights till 12am & then got up for school the next morning. For the last 10 years I’ve been telling my kids per @daveramsey that when it’s time to buy their very 1st car I would split it with them. Meaning, I will match you dollar for dollar as much as you save up. Well today my 15 yr old daughter handed over 6k and said you got my money bitch?! 🤣🤣🤣
